{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource\/initwithidentifier:configurationurl:"]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"}],"title":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNRasterTileSource(im)initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource\/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a raster tile source initialized with an identifier and configuration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"URL."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"identifier","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"configurationURL","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"identifier","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A string that uniquely identifies the source in the style to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"which it is added.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"configurationURL","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A URL to a TileJSON configuration file describing the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source’s contents and other metadata."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An initialized raster tile source.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After initializing and configuring the source, add it to a map view’s style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"using the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL may be a full HTTP or HTTPS URL or canonical URL. The URL should","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point to a JSON file that conforms to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TileJSON specification","type":"text"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If a Mapbox URL is specified, this source uses a tile size of 256. For all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other tilesets, the default value is 512. (See the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" documentation for more information about tile"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes.) If you need to use a tile size other than the default, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:tileSize:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterTileSource":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies raster image tiles"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to be shown on the map. The location of and metadata about the tiles are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"defined either by an option dictionary or by an external file that conforms to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TileJSON specification"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A raster tile source is added to an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object along with one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterStyleLayer","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects. Use a raster style layer to control the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"appearance of content supplied by the raster tile source."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNRasterTileSource","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNRasterTileSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle/addSource:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds a new source to the current style."}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"addSource:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle\/addsource:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addSource:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"addSource:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntilesourceoptiontilesize","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","title":"MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object containing a floating-point number that specifies the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"width and height (measured in points) at which the map displays each raster","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"image tile when the map’s zoom level is an integer. The raster tile source","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"scales its images up or down when the map’s zoom level falls between two","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"integers.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterStyleLayer":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterStyleLayer","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a style layer that renders georeferenced raster"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"imagery on the map, especially raster tiles."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterStyleLayer","title":"MLNRasterStyleLayer","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNRasterStyleLayer"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrasterstylelayer","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterTileSource/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource\/initwithidentifier:configurationurl:","role":"symbol","title":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a raster tile source initialized with an identifier and configuration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"URL."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource\/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy object for the current map style."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNStyle"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle","title":"MLNStyle","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"}}}